title: Little Devil Teemo Icon
body:
Okay , so i played a couple of Doom bot game, probably like 5-6 and i won a couple game too, but i still havent recieved the Little Devil Teemo Icon, and i was wondering why , i mean you can see in my name that i kinda like {{champion:17}} , and was wondering if its still possible to obtain it, oh and i didnt get the pumpkin either, and i've sent a mystery skin to my friend The Red Pelican.
Thank you for your time - Teemo
